# ABP — Build & QA Checklists

> **When to apply:** Run the relevant section at each lifecycle gate. Attach when reviewing a component, prepping a deployment, or auditing accessibility. Not needed during initial scaffolding.

---

## Build Order

```
1. styles/design-tokens.css + app/globals.css
2. app/layout.tsx (font loading, metadata)
3. EditorialLine.tsx        ← used everywhere; build first
4. Hero.tsx
5. IndexRow.tsx
6. MediaFeature.tsx → NewsGrid.tsx
7. StoryCard.tsx → OffsetGrid.tsx
8. SundayDinner.tsx, Donations.tsx
9. ui/SocialButton.tsx → Footer.tsx
10. app/page.tsx (assembly)
11. app/about/page.tsx, app/events/page.tsx, app/donate/page.tsx
12. .github/workflows/azure-static-web-apps.yml
```

---

## Component Build Checklist

Run for every component before moving to the next.

### Structure
- [ ] File name matches spec exactly (`Hero.tsx` not `HeroSection.tsx`)
- [ ] TypeScript strict — explicit prop interface, no `any` types
- [ ] All text copied verbatim from content spec — no paraphrasing

### Styling
- [ ] Zero hardcoded hex values — all colors via CSS variables
- [ ] All fonts via `var(--font-display / --font-body / --font-heading-ui / --font-micro)`
- [ ] Font-weight ≥ 450 everywhere (target 500)
- [ ] No text below 9px (micro minimum: 9.5px)
- [ ] Glassmorphism cards: `var(--color-card-surface)` + `backdrop-filter: blur(4px)`
- [ ] Borders: `var(--color-border)` or `var(--color-divider)` — never `#ccc` or `gray`

### Motion
- [ ] Hover: `transform` and `color`/`background` over `0.25s ease` only
- [ ] Reveal: `opacity` + `translateY` via IntersectionObserver
- [ ] `prefers-reduced-motion` block present in globals.css
- [ ] `html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }` in globals.css

### Images
- [ ] `next/image` for all images (never raw `<img>`)
- [ ] Hero brand mark has `priority` prop
- [ ] `width`/`height` or `fill`+`sizes` on every `<Image>`
- [ ] Path uses leading slash: `/assets/abp/imgs/…`

---

## Accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA + Dyslexia-Aware)

### Keyboard
- [ ] All interactive elements Tab-reachable in visual order
- [ ] Focus ring always visible — never `outline: none` without replacement
- [ ] Custom hover interactions have focus equivalents
- [ ] Skip-to-content link present

### Screen Reader
- [ ] One `<h1>` per page; heading levels not skipped
- [ ] All images have `alt` (descriptive on content, `""` on decorative)
- [ ] `SocialButton` has `aria-label`
- [ ] `<nav aria-label="…">` on navigation landmarks

### Visual Contrast
- [ ] `--color-text` (#52325b) on gradient ≥ 4.5:1
- [ ] `--color-text-muted` (#76547d) on gradient ≥ 4.5:1
- [ ] White on `--color-primary` (#7c2d86) ≥ 4.5:1
- [ ] Color is not the only state indicator

### Dyslexia-Aware Typography
- [ ] Body copy: Lexend (reading ease)
- [ ] UI labels/headings: Comic Relief (distinct letterforms)
- [ ] Tiny metadata: Atkinson Hyperlegible
- [ ] Line-height ≥ 1.5 on body paragraphs
- [ ] No justified text alignment
- [ ] Paragraph `max-width` ≤ 72ch

### Touch & Mobile
- [ ] All tap targets ≥ 44×44px
- [ ] No hover-only UI patterns

---

## Performance Checklist

- [ ] `'use client'` only where browser APIs/hooks required
- [ ] `priority` on Hero `<Image>` (LCP candidate)
- [ ] All fonts loaded via `next/font/google` — not CDN `<link>` tags
- [ ] `display: 'swap'` on all font configs
- [ ] IntersectionObserver cleanup runs on unmount
- [ ] `images.unoptimized: false` in `next.config.js`

### Core Web Vitals Targets
| Metric | Target |
|---|---|
| LCP | < 2.5s |
| INP | < 200ms |
| CLS | < 0.1 |
| Lighthouse Performance | ≥ 85 |
| Lighthouse Accessibility | ≥ 90 |

---

## Azure Deployment Checklist

### `next.config.js`
- [ ] No `output: 'export'`
- [ ] `images.unoptimized: false`
- [ ] No `output: 'standalone'` unless bundle demands it

### GitHub Actions (`azure-static-web-apps.yml`)
- [ ] `app_location: "/"`
- [ ] `api_location: ""`
- [ ] `output_location: ""` (empty)
- [ ] `AZURE_STATIC_WEB_APPS_API_TOKEN` secret set in repo

### Repo
- [ ] `.gitignore` includes `.next` and `node_modules`
- [ ] No `.env` files committed
- [ ] No `staticwebapp.config.json` with `navigationFallback` → `index.html`

