## Pre-Merge Review

### Content Fidelity
- [ ] All 6 IndexRow items in correct order with exact dates/categories
- [ ] All 4 MediaFeature cards: correct image path, title, external URL
- [ ] Footer email: `auntbecksplacebaltimore@gmail.com`
- [ ] Footer socials: `facebook.com/AuntBecksPlace/` + `instagram.com/auntbecksplace/`
- [ ] Copyright: `Aunt Becks Place ©2026`

### Cross-Device
- [ ] Desktop (1280px+): offset grid, hover states
- [ ] Tablet (768px): grid transitions
- [ ] Mobile (375px): single-column, hero `clamp(2.4rem, 10vw, 4rem)`, touch targets ≥ 44px

### Design System
- [ ] `design-tokens.css` contains all required variables
- [ ] No inline `style={{ color: '#...' }}` with raw hex

### ADR — Document When You
- Change `next.config.js` structure
- Add a new npm dependency
- Deviate from the component architecture spec

---

## Boundaries Reference

| Always | Ask First | Never |
|---|---|---|
| CSS variables for all color/font refs | Add a new npm dependency | `output: 'export'` |
| Font-weight ≥ 450 | Change `next.config.js` structure | Commit `.next/` |
| Semantic HTML over `<div>` | Add `staticwebapp.config.json` entries | Hardcode hex colors |
| `rel="noopener noreferrer"` on external links | Modify `.github/workflows/` | Tailwind or CSS frameworks |
| `alt` on every image | Alter asset file names or paths | `navigationFallback` catch-all |
